Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:12.33,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是連前進軌道都無法改變的幾率
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:16.86,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有百分之一就要奮起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:20.70,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟、被「命運」所束縛的人生、不 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:27.38,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要將它重寫、因為若能看見你和未來 不是最棒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:30.48,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧！我只想在戰鬥中成長 HEY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:31.31,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,擊穿陰天！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:34.48,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我的烈焰仍舊熊熊燃燒 雷鳴撕裂天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:38.32,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想消除夢魘 看見未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:40.79,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,過去、未來、還有如今當下、
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:43.78,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不畏懼過去 現在為了被托付的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:45.13,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吼出我的驕傲!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:51.80,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不想看到眼淚、所以要不斷嘶吼！一直永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:55.80,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會墮落！因為揚起的風會讓我凌駕於命運之上！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:03:02.18,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因為身後、有著想要守護的笑容！ 永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.65,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,為了彼此！我會揍飛你心中的痛苦！讓悲傷什麼的永遠安息！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:09.78,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,832)}無論多少次…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:34.95,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,月光搖曳 我們未來的藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:42.17,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天會實現 描繪明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:47.01,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠不會磨滅 銘記在心中的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.01,0:22:55.81,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,若是無盡的淚水能掩蓋傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:04.82,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,那就無需畏懼 再次去相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:13.32,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,向著無邊無際的天空 張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:19.16,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不再哭泣 仰望天空中那輪皎月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:24.96,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,即使心存悲傷 也要懷著希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:29.30,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算無法回頭 也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:35.93,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生輝的夢想 閃耀在探索的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:41.94,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,最寶貴的那份思念 仍舊在延續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:47.78,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,無論哪裏 我們都一起走過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:55.45,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,825)}握住那唯一的心靈之匙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的希望之門打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝利之門打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來 未來就能得救了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從未來而來的露西小姐也能安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能打開門
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須現在立刻關上門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在立刻關上門 那扇門不能打開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大門會關上 這是已經決定好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:51.79,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(640,450)\fad(524,0}連我的份一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關上門 立刻馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 這是對抗大龍群的唯一兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果現在關上門的話 日蝕·加農炮將無法發射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼日蝕·加農炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是一扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連結時間的門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將自身積蓄的魔力釋放出來的武器就是日蝕·加農炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 那根本不是什麼武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再說下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然會受到公主的懲戒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那扇大門是連接400年前的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地面震動得好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力？不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是城堡的方向 也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個日蝕啟動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍…從門裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是城堡的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然如此強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑吧 這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能打得過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有一頭出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事啊 又有龍冒出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門要怎樣才能關上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快說啊 現在不是發呆的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那邊的底座上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,底座 就是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要搬動這個扳手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用星靈魔法師的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一萬頭龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是從門裏出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西 你剛剛是察覺到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我 是克魯爺爺一直在調查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就在剛才終於完成了對這個門的分析
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是將澤雷夫之書的魔法和星靈魔法相調和而成的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來是可以通過指定時間的坐標來進行時間移動的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天是個例外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個月亮會擾亂它的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法錯亂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 這扇門才會失去控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它和400年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是和龍族仍然存活的時代連接到了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話…和之前說的不一樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是…如何形容這樣的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的吧 這樣的有一萬頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快散開 找個地方隱蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則會被一舉擊潰的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又出來一頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是岩石 岩石在動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西 門還是關不上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍一頭接一頭的跑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼關不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 這裏危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於我錯誤的決策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界迎來了終結…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界…將被龍的憤怒浸染
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:10:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要連另一個我的份兒一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連我的份一起歡笑 一起哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個地震…難道已經？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答應過她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守護未來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有龍從門裏出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點關上門的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 這裏很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請快點迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 請抓緊時間迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這究竟是做了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西 快點把門關上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星靈魔法師的力量不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西小姐 請拿出黃道十二門的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我的鑰匙一起 用十二把鑰匙把門封印吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用星靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鑰匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發出金光…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃道十二門的星靈們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請借給我封印邪惡之物的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開啟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二門的門扉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃道十二宮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 所有的星靈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要高興還太早了 出來了幾頭龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七 七頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得不錯啊 露西 雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有七頭龍就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格…大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話 我還真控制不了一萬頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個人…告知了我未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是欺騙了公主的未來人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你最開始的目的就是這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好聽著 愚民們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在開始 人類的時代宣告終結
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來即將展開的是龍的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為開始 就將這個城鎮裏的所有魔法師殺個乾淨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍聽那傢伙的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛他說控制什麼的…難道說？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是支配龍的秘術 操龍魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支配龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙的目的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做這種事有什麼好處…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏就交給你了 基爾柯尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是挺好吃的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在龍之墓地見到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這 這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體是由火焰構成的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進攻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固定好腳邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按計劃好的做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾名為阿特拉斯弗萊姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓汝等見識地獄之炎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅持住 小鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍齒之虎總攻擊 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盯著嘴裏 肚子 那些好像很軟的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Man 這就是真正的龍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不能退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在才是展現我們藍色天馬實力的好時機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用人數壓倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有魔力全放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點傷都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中一點攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃這招 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好結實的生物 任何魔法都不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中攻擊某一點試試如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大家協作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我先砍他一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂殿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 快散開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Man
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然施加了防禦力下降的香氣 還是沒用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Man
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 連一點擦傷都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱗片居然如此堅固
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類是否能打倒龍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再肆虐一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們看看龍之怒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏·多拉格尼爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:24:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 那麼強大的龍居然有七頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 哈比 嚇尿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.42,0:24:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱才沒有害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.08,0:24:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是正好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍有七頭 我們這邊也有七位滅龍魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？ 不是只有六位滅龍魔法師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 數個數你都不會麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把我當傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有第七位在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 七頭龍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.64,0:24:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的一位 怎麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.31,0:24:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？ 莫非是那個傢伙？

